# Types & Interfaces

The following types and interfaces are used throughout the Core MFE:

- `IUser` — User object
- `IAuthToken` — Auth token object
- `ILoginResponse`, `ILoginAsResponse` — Auth API responses
- `IUserSessionResponse` — User session API response
- `IAuthModuleConfig`, `ITenantModuleConfig`, `IVerbiageModuleConfig` — Module configs
- `IPayload`, `IRequestOptions` — API payloads and options
- `IUseApi<T>` — Generic API composable interface
- `ITenant`, `ILocalizationLanguage`, `IAddress`, `IExtraData` — Tenant and localization
- `IVerbiageInfo`, `IVerbiageResponse`, `IVerbiageLastUpdateResponse`, `IVerbiageLocalesResponse` — Verbiage/i18n

See `src/types.ts` for full definitions and usage examples. 